snippet.title: Best VGM 1964 - Kirby & The Rainbow Curse - The Wild Red Yonder
snippet.description:
See also:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii U
Kirby & The Rainbow Curse (2015)
The Wild Red Yonder
Shogo Sakai
